<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - ChatApp</title>
    <style>
        * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
}

header {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    color: white;
}

nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.nav-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
}

.nav-links li {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
}

.nav-links a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
}

.nav-links .btn {
    background-color: #007bff;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

.nav-links .btn:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
}

main {
    flex: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
    padding: 2rem;
}

.about-hero {
    
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.about-hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.history, .features, .team {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    text-align: center;
}

.history h2, .features h2, .team h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.history p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.features-container, .team-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.feature-item, .team-member {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    margin: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 300px;
    text-align: center;
}

.feature-item h3, .team-member h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.feature-item p, .team-member p {
    font-size: 1rem;
}

.team-member img {
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

footer {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 0;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">ChatApp</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="#login" class="btn">Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="about-hero">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Discover the story behind ChatApp and meet the team dedicated to connecting people around the world.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="history">
            <h2>Our Journey</h2>
            <p>ChatApp started as a small project with a big vision: to make communication seamless and accessible for everyone. Over the years, we have grown into a robust platform used by millions worldwide.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="features" id="features">
            <h2>Core Features</h2>
            <div class="features-container">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Real-time Messaging</h3>
                    <p>Send and receive messages instantly with our real-time messaging feature.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Secure Conversations</h3>
                    <p>Your privacy is our priority. All conversations are encrypted for maximum security.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Cross-Platform Support</h3>
                    <p>Stay connected on any device, whether it's a smartphone, tablet, or desktop.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="team">
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team-container">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="team-member1.jpg" alt="Team Member 1">
                    <h3>John Doe</h3>
                    <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="team-member2.jpg" alt="Team Member 2">
                    <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                    <p>Chief Technology Officer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="team-member3.jpg" alt="Team Member 3">
                    <h3>Mike Johnson</h3>
                    <p>Lead Developer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 ChatApp. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
